Package: XSitu
Type: Package
Title: Ex-Situ conservation status
Description: This package implements a method to evaluate the ex-situ conservation status of a species. The method is described in: El Graoui, M., M.E. Ghanem, M. Amri, R.J. Hijmans, 2025. A distance-based framework for assessing the ex-situ conservation status of plants. Submitted for publication. 
Version: 1.1-0
Date: 2025-03-26
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports: terra, igraph
Maintainer: Robert Hijmans <r.hijmans@gmail.com>
Encoding: UTF-8
License: GPL (>=3)
BugReports: https://github.com/rspatial/terra/issues/
LazyLoad: yes
Authors@R: c(
	person("Marwa", "El Graoui", role="aut"),
    person("Robert J.", "Hijmans", role=c("cre", "aut"), email="r.hijmans@gmail.com", comment=c(ORCID = "0000-0003-2392-6140")))
